// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1622 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: a9982b71-687f-5e83-91d2-48b980b4740a

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:5* OR ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:6*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
